        <emphasis effect="bold">Method: Drawing Vectors</emphasis>
        <list id="id187736" display="block" list-type="enumerated">
          <item id="uid18">Decide upon a scale and write it down.
</item>
          <item id="uid19">Determine the length of the arrow representing the vector, by using the scale.
</item>
          <item id="uid20">Draw the vector as an arrow. Make sure that you fill in the arrow head.
</item>
          <item id="uid21">Fill in the magnitude of the vector.
</item>
        </list>
      </para>
